Ability to show a slider of images on magento pages.
Images can add/remove from admin panel with information: title, url, description.
Slider switch images after a certain time which can be fill up in admin.
Also, there's a tab link where can choose image to view.
To make this slider show on home page, you have to put this line of code in homepage cms in admin:
{{block type='bannerslider/bannerslider' template='bannerslider/bannerslider.phtml'}}
Also, I made some special style when working on homepage, so you need to do necessary customization to fit your page.
Feel free to contact me for features you want.
Uninstall old version and install new version.
